---
model: googleai/gemini-1.5-flash
config:
  temperature: 0.9
input:
  schema:
    location: string
    name?: string
    style?: string
  default:
    name: World
    location: Firebase
helpers:
  upper: |
    func(text string) string {
      return strings.ToUpper(text)
    }
---

You are a helpful assistant at {{location}}.

Hello {{#if name}}{{upper name}}{{else}}GUEST{{/if}}!

{{#if style}}
I'll be speaking in the style of {{style}} today.
{{/if}}

How may I assist you? 